The Judicial Commission of Inquiry into allegations of State Capture, Corruption and Fraud in the Public Sector including Organs of State continues on Thursday. * Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. JOHANNESBURG - The Zondo Commission will hear evidence related to the ANN7 broadcast channel and state capture on Thursday. READ: Inside ANN7: The Bad and the ugly The Commission is expected to hear evidence from former Household Manager at Mahlamba Ndlopfu, Ramaru Mekgwe; current Household Manager at Mahlamba Ndlopfu, Jacques Human and former SABC journalist Gillian Pillay.